00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:40,420
It looks like she was an addict.

111
00:04:40,420 --> 00:04:43,180
No LKAs in years other than the place that she died.

112
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:44,460
- You locate the family? - Yeah.

