115
00:04:48,450 --> 00:04:50,450
Written her off as dead a long time ago.

116
00:04:50,450 --> 00:04:53,070
- Won't be claiming the body. - And what about Billy?

117
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:54,810
Oh, with him, I had to do some digging.

118
00:04:54,810 --> 00:04:57,400
Alderman Braddem never mentions Billy in his stump speeches.

119
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,500
Kid's never one of the sons

120
00:04:58,500 --> 00:04:59,780
