156
00:06:16,050 --> 00:06:18,750
- To get sober. - Or to rehearse.

157
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:22,970
Look. We're gonna treat his kid like any other offender.

158
00:06:23,060 --> 00:06:25,620
You take his blood, you document his tox,

