231
00:09:33,070 --> 00:09:34,890
We got two sets of takeout

232
00:09:34,890 --> 00:09:37,780
and beers surrounding two chairs.

233
00:09:38,220 --> 00:09:40,630
- Two sets of the works. - Not much here.

234
00:09:42,590 --> 00:09:43,720
This place is tiny.

235
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,350
I know, I really don't see

236
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:48,010
how somebody could be hiding out.

237
00:09:48,810 --> 00:09:52,080
And the blood splatter indicates just one offender.

239
00:09:53,250 --> 00:09:54,990
TV was on at the time of death.

240
00:09:54,990 --> 00:09:57,090
Yeah, Forensics hasn't dusted this room yet.

241
00:09:58,220 --> 00:10:02,160
They are expected to rise based on positive...

242
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:03,410
We just wanted to circle back,

243
00:10:03,410 --> 00:10:05,090
make sure Patrol didn't miss anything.

244
00:10:05,090 --> 00:10:07,350
You see anything unusual? Any visitors?

245
00:10:07,350 --> 00:10:09,550
- The car was unusual. - A car?

246
00:10:09,620 --> 00:10:12,450
All right. What car is that?

247
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:13,970
I don't know. It looked blue, maybe?

248
00:10:13,970 --> 00:10:16,160
2:00 A.M., it just sat out there wasting gas.

249
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:17,590
Headlights blaring through my window.

250
00:10:17,590 --> 00:10:18,740
Did you see anyone in the car,

251
00:10:18,740 --> 00:10:20,510
or anyone enter or exit the apartment?

252
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:22,900
No, just the car. I took my dog out.

253
00:10:22,900 --> 00:10:24,510
By the time I came back, it sped away,

254
00:10:24,510 --> 00:10:26,150
but it sat out there 20 minutes.

255
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:27,330
Why didn't you mention this to Patrol?

256
00:10:27,330 --> 00:10:29,330
No Patrol ever came by. I've been home all day.

257
00:10:29,340 --> 00:10:30,640
Nobody's talked to me.

258
00:10:30,850 --> 00:10:32,160
She died, didn't she?

259
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:34,250
- That young girl? - Yes, ma'am.

260
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:36,580
She seemed like a good person.

261
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:38,700
Seemed like she tried real hard to be happy.

262
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:42,470
I don't understand. Where is my son?

263
00:10:42,470 --> 00:10:44,750
- Sir, your son's upstairs. - Upstairs.

264
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:47,120
You've got him in a box? You found him high?

265
00:10:47,730 --> 00:10:48,990
Yes, sir. He was high.

266
00:10:48,990 --> 00:10:51,080
