267
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:52,340
while he's high.

268
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:53,670
Are you kidding me?

269
00:10:54,250 --> 00:10:56,060
Why the hell is he upstairs without a lawyer?

270
00:10:56,060 --> 00:10:58,620
- Listen, I'm happy to talk-- - I am gonna have your badge.

271
00:10:58,620 --> 00:11:01,200
- I'm just doing my job. - You won't be for much longer.

272
00:11:01,220 --> 00:11:03,160
