279
00:11:17,490 --> 00:11:18,450
Right this way.

280
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:25,990
I'll speak to you upstairs.

281
00:11:31,350 --> 00:11:33,130
McKenzie, you just came here to watch?

282
00:11:43,540 --> 00:11:45,410
That was clearly leaked to Alderman.

283
00:11:45,410 --> 00:11:47,530
Well, it doesn't matter how. We're here now.

284
00:11:47,830 --> 00:11:49,390
Tell me we got something.

